<p>Palettes of well-defined colors are coordinated to create color schemes that spark our imagination. Within these schemes one color is chosen to represent the new year. Fresh, revitilizing, and provoking, this color is the creative sum of all things in the design industry. Just as the year is ready to renew itself, so is our inspiration with these color predictions. </p> 
