<p>Pantone has announced their Color of the Year for 2015 to be 'Marsala'. A warm and ruddy red-brown, Marsala dances the line between impactful and subtle. Taking cues from its namesake wine, this shade of fortified red emanates a sophisticated but natural earthiness. Sultry and full-bodied, these qualities encourage experimentation. Universally appealing, Marsala is a grounded statement color that will translate well into any design. </p>
