<p>Benjamin Moore has chosen 'Guilford Green' as their 2015 Color of the Year. Out of their Historic Color collection, this shade of silvery green is steeped in tradition. Tried and true, Guilford Green is a confident classic that delivers timeless color to any design. Its lush and luminous appearance gracefully matches to nearly any palette. Refined yet romantic, Guilford Green is the new natural neutral. </p>
